comments: Avdija (WAS) brings his hand toward James' (LAL) right side and marginal contact occurs as James pivots along the perimeter.
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) brings his arm toward Anthony's (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs with Anthony's front as he starts his dribble.
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) rests his hand on Anthony's (LAL) back and quickly releases away without applying any force as Anthony starts his upward shooting motion.
Avdija (WAS) and Reaves (LAL) come together at the same spot in the lane and marginal body contact occurs before Avdija deflects the ball away.
Correctly called 24 second violation. The shot clock expires prior to the ball landing out of bounds.
Porzingis (WAS) and Westbrook (LAL) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Westbrook (LAL) legally contests Porzingis' (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Avdija (WAS) and Bradley (LAL) engage and disengage with one another as the defensive switch takes place during the pick.
Smith (WAS) moves alongside James' (LAL) path on the perimeter and marginal contact occurs with James' slightly extended off-arm as Smith attempts to deflect the ball.
Bradley (LAL) is already in Avdija's (WAS) path when contact occurs and he gives Avdija time and distance to avoid the contact.
Porzingis (WAS) and Reaves (LAL) come together at the same spot near the elbow and incidental body contact occurs as Reaves moves to contest the jump shot attempt.
Anthony (LAL) is already in Satoransky's (WAS) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Monk (LAL) brings his off-arm toward Satoransky's (WAS) front and marginal contact occurs as Monk releases away toward the perimeter.
Satoransky (WAS) legally contests Monk's (LAL) jump shot attempt. After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor of a 3-point basket stood as called.
James (LAL) and Porzingis (WAS) briefly engage and disengage as Porzingis moves to set the pick.
Westbrook (LAL) legally contests Porzingis' (WAS) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Avdija (WAS) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Reaves (LAL) commits a take foul on Caldwell-Pope (WAS).
Avdija (WAS) and Anthony (LAL) briefly engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Avdija (WAS) brushes Anthony's (LAL) right arm and quickly retreats it away without applying any force prior to the start of Anthony's upward shooting motion.
Avdija (WAS) legally contests Anthony's (LAL) jump shot attempt. Any marginal body contact that occurs during the follow-through is the result of Anthony drifting forward toward Avdija.
Correctly called 24 second violation. The game clock was re-set to 0.2.
